data.description: Price Improvement!!! Motivated Seller's!! Come take a look at this great home in the established Wheeler Creek Addition. 3 Bedroom, 2 bath with a 2 car garage. HVAC was replaced 2 years ago and the roof was replaced approximately 4 yrs ago. Don't miss the opportunity to live in a great house in a wonderful neighborhood. Storage shed in the backyard will convey with the property.
